N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 15 ยง 19.11 - Effective date

State Regulations

This Part shall take effect five days after filing with the

Secretary of State and shall apply to applications for original registrations
filed on or after October 1, 1974, and to applications for renewals of
registrations expiring on or after October 31, 1974. Notes
